    <title>在AD域中启用ldaps协议</title>
    <url>/post/f918b20a.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>本文介绍如何在AD域名中启用ldaps协议<br><a id="more"></a></p><h3 id="一、准备工作"><a href="#一、准备工作" class="headerlink" title="一、准备工作"></a>一、准备工作</h3><p>首先需要安装git和cmder工具，下载地址如下：<br>git for windows<br><a href="https://git-scm.com/download/win" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://git-scm.com/download/win</a><br>cmder mini<br><a href="https://github.com/cmderdev/cmder/releases/download/v1.3.11/cmder_mini.zip" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/cmderdev/cmder/releases/download/v1.3.11/cmder_mini.zip</a></p><h3 id="二、启用ldaps"><a href="#二、启用ldaps" class="headerlink" title="二、启用ldaps"></a>二、启用ldaps</h3><p>(1)创建ca根证书<br></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">openssl genrsa -des3 -out ca.key 4096</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><img src="http://cdn.jier.site/2019-05-27_165848.png" alt=""><p></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">openssl req -new -x509 -days 3650 -key ca.key -out ca.crt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如下：只需要填Common Name为ad域(jier.site)<br><img src="http://cdn.jier.site/2019-05-27_165936.png" alt=""></p><p>(2)导入ca根证书到本地计算机<br>执行命令certlm.msc，打开本地计算机的证书控制台<br><img src="http://cdn.jier.site/2019-05-27_170612.png" alt=""></p><p>导入ca根证书到”本地计算机\受信任的根证书颁发机构”<br><img src="http://cdn.jier.site/2019-05-27_170633.png" alt=""></p><p>(3)生成request.inf<br>如下：指定CN为本地计算机全名<br><img src="http://cdn.jier.site/2019-05-27_171029.png" alt=""></p><p>内容如下：<br></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[Version]</span><br><span class="line">Signature=<span class="string">"<span class="variable">$Windows</span> NT$"</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[NewRequest]</span><br><span class="line">Subject = <span class="string">"CN=Ethan.jier.site"</span></span><br><span class="line">KeySpec = 1</span><br><span class="line">KeyLength = 1024</span><br><span class="line">Exportable = TRUE</span><br><span class="line">MachineKeySet = TRUE</span><br><span class="line">SMIME = FALSE</span><br><span class="line">PrivateKeyArchive = FALSE</span><br><span class="line">UserProtected = FALSE</span><br><span class="line">UseExistingKeySet = FALSE</span><br><span class="line">ProviderName = <span class="string">"Microsoft RSA SChannel Cryptographic Provider"</span></span><br><span class="line">ProviderType = 12</span><br><span class="line">RequestType = PKCS10</span><br><span class="line">KeyUsage = 0xa0</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[EnhancedKeyUsageExtension]</span><br><span class="line">OID = 1.3.6.1.5.5.7.3.1 ; Server Authentication</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><p>(4)生成client.csr<br></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">certreq -new request.inf client.csr</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><img src="http://cdn.jier.site/2019-05-27_171302.png" alt=""><p></p><p>(5)生成v3ext.txt<br><img src="http://cdn.jier.site/2019-05-27_171357.png" alt=""></p><p>内容如下：<br></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">keyUsage=digitalSignature,keyEncipherment</span><br><span class="line">extendedKeyUsage=serverAuth</span><br><span class="line">subjectKeyIdentifier=<span class="built_in">hash</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><p>(6)生成client.crt<br></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">openssl x509 -req -days 3650 -<span class="keyword">in</span> client.csr -CA ca.crt -CAkey ca.key -extfile v3ext.txt -set_serial 01 -out client.crt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><img src="http://cdn.jier.site/2019-05-27_171435.png" alt=""><p></p><p>(7)导入客户端证书<br></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">certreq -accept client.crt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><img src="http://cdn.jier.site/2019-05-27_171729.png" alt=""><p></p><p>(8)生成ldap-renewservercert.txt<br><img src="http://cdn.jier.site/2019-05-27_171730.png" alt=""><br>内容如下：<br></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dn:</span><br><span class="line">changetype: modify</span><br><span class="line">add: renewServerCertificate</span><br><span class="line">renewServerCertificate: 1</span><br><span class="line">-</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><p>(9)刷新ad域名证书配置<br></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ldifde -i -f ldap-renewservercert.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><img src="http://cdn.jier.site/2019-05-27_171744.png" alt=""><p></p><p>(10)使用LdapAdmin测试连接<br><img src="http://cdn.jier.site/2019-05-27_171906.png" alt=""></p><h3 id="三、参考链接"><a href="#三、参考链接" class="headerlink" title="三、参考链接"></a>三、参考链接</h3><p><a href="http://www.javaxt.com/tutorials/windows/how_to_enable_ldaps_in_active_directory" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://www.javaxt.com/tutorials/windows/how_to_enable_ldaps_in_active_directory</a><br><a href="https://gist.github.com/magnetikonline/0ccdabfec58eb1929c997d22e7341e45" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://gist.github.com/magnetikonline/0ccdabfec58eb1929c997d22e7341e45</a></p>]]></content>
